    </node>
    <node id="Sunlight">
      <data key="d0">Sunlight</data>
      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">Sunlight causes symptoms in PLE.&lt;SEP&gt;Sunlight is a major risk factor for developing melanoma, and reducing exposure to it can help prevent the disease.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-185e181fe87408ed68fffee05c4bf2c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7be69385a3c09d3b0d51dbc9a40450e1</data>
