    <node id="Inflammation">
      <data key="d0">Inflammation</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Inflammation is a common response of the body's immune system to damage or infection.&lt;SEP&gt;A bodily response to injury or infection, which can be treated by reducing inflammation with medication like Aspirin.&lt;SEP&gt;Inflammation is a bodily response that is reduced by Aspirin.&lt;SEP&gt;Inflammation is a bodily response to injury or infection.&lt;SEP&gt;Inflammation is a natural response of the body's immune system.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c62e0e5e965a5609d60ac725c7a40a57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a45c0433e861eaa94dbda4172985c8d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e349119c3189688316f142a76b2f2e86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96246f0053db41bc6854767c93a37e6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c01ebde56aad2ac664ce27bcf95cd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-073142c11014525a0c579f8afe5d210b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2f9f6e0c1ac72f2d9f132ba1b3ab8be3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68fbdd19f58d875a928b1cc8cc41cea7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2258cc9d8db0680e066bcf3b3675f10c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a108389c3f299fd71255c81b03305b55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c675cb429137f1eae8fe9eda77046b5b</data>
