    </node>
    <node id="Lymphadenopathy">
      <data key="d0">Lymphadenopathy</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">The enlargement of lymph nodes in the neck or armpits, potentially indicative of infection or inflammation related to liver disease.&lt;SEP&gt;Lymphadenopathy is a condition characterized by the enlargement of lymph nodes, which can be due to various underlying etiologies.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a45c0433e861eaa94dbda4172985c8d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-052d9f2eb36a76fdb7920ef60341853c</data>
