      <data key="d0">Swelling of hands and feet</data>
      <data key="d1">clinicaldetail</data>
      <data key="d2">A condition where an individual experiences swelling in their limbs due to fluid retention, often associated with liver disease or other underlying conditions affecting circulation.</data>
