    <node id="Acute Otitis Media">
      <data key="d0">Acute Otitis Media</data>
      <data key="d1">disease</data>
      <data key="d2">Acute Otitis Media is a middle ear infection characterized by symptoms such as fever, irritability, and hearing loss. It primarily affects children and is caused by either bacterial or viral infections. Treatment typically involves antibiotics like Amoxicillin to combat the underlying cause of the infection. Untreated acute otitis media can lead to complications, including permanent hearing loss. The condition is usually treated with a course of antibiotics, such as Amoxicillin, to alleviate symptoms and prevent further complications.

It's worth noting that there may be variations in treatment approaches depending on the specific type and severity of the infection. However, antibiotics remain the primary treatment for acute otitis media.&lt;SEP&gt;Acute otitis media is a condition that requires prompt treatment to prevent complications.&lt;SEP&gt;Acute otitis media is a middle ear infection treated with Amoxicillin and Aspirin but also sometimes with Warfarin, which may cause gastrointestinal bleeding as an adverse outcome in patients with certain conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Acute otitis media is a middle ear infection treated with antibiotics like Amoxicillin.&lt;SEP&gt;Acute otitis media is a type of ear infection that affects children.&lt;SEP&gt;Acute otitis media is a middle ear infection treated with antibiotics like Amoxicillin.&lt;SEP&gt;Acute otitis media is a middle ear infection treated with Amoxicillin.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a45c0433e861eaa94dbda4172985c8d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17717aab6acc128a83824d9e8317ea4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2f8e3840cde7d092cb7e453428087efd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e29dee1ec3e83daa8c3982ec784f54d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa7b0387cb6903fcd84f7bdac107fe37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d4798197d2ae5bc5e60e5d876f94f20&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69b807472f4820ade4cbf3153e7e88b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0392546b4be8990b5651990bc3c882c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ba9ca889a884bf086782a96a1c01374&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c01ebde56aad2ac664ce27bcf95cd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-073142c11014525a0c579f8afe5d210b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2f9dbbcfc70eb17be913a3d7973ef92e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2789d641115d5adedba14603fd459ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0535e5dee668fb3fd6a4787bb7b0a649&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbac6ca9c4de60d11284fef00668f6dc</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1776248401</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Antibiotics">
