      <data key="d1">activeingredient</data>
      <data key="d2">Antibiotics are medications prescribed to treat bacterial infections, which include acute otitis media.&lt;SEP&gt;Amoxicillin belongs to the class of antibiotics used for treating acute otitis media.</data>
