      <data key="d3">chunk-a45c0433e861eaa94dbda4172985c8d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a037de6f2fcc6d8499a41fc6d0ae4590&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa7b0387cb6903fcd84f7bdac107fe37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d4798197d2ae5bc5e60e5d876f94f20&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69b807472f4820ade4cbf3153e7e88b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0392546b4be8990b5651990bc3c882c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-073142c11014525a0c579f8afe5d210b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2789d641115d5adedba14603fd459ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0535e5dee668fb3fd6a4787bb7b0a649&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbac6ca9c4de60d11284fef00668f6dc</data>
      <data key="d2">The dosage of Amoxicillin is typically adjusted based on age and weight.&lt;SEP&gt;Pediatric patients are a target demographic for specific dosing guidelines.&lt;SEP&gt;Pediatric patients are the target demographic for this specific dosing guideline.&lt;SEP&gt;Pediatric patients are the target demographic for specific dosing guidelines and treatments.&lt;SEP&gt;Pediatric patients are the target demographic for this specific dosing guideline.&lt;SEP&gt;Pediatric patients are a target demographic for specific dosing guidelines like the one for Amoxicillin.</data>
