    <node id="Penicillin Allergy">
      <data key="d0">Penicillin Allergy</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a45c0433e861eaa94dbda4172985c8d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa7b0387cb6903fcd84f7bdac107fe37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0392546b4be8990b5651990bc3c882c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fc0ac2cbfbe29731925a257279ee8f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0535e5dee668fb3fd6a4787bb7b0a649</data>
      <data key="d2">Patients with a penicillin allergy may experience severe reactions to Amoxicillin.&lt;SEP&gt;A history of penicillin allergy increases the risk of allergic reactions in patients taking Amoxicillin.&lt;SEP&gt;A history of penicillin allergy increases the risk of allergic reactions to certain medications like Amoxicillin.&lt;SEP&gt;Individuals who experience an allergic reaction to penicillin should avoid taking SSRI medications.&lt;SEP&gt;A history of penicillin allergy increases the risk of adverse reactions such as a dry cough when taking Amoxicillin.</data>
      <data key="d1">disease</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1776247084</data>
      <data key="d6" />
