    <node id="Lassa Fever">
      <data key="d0">Lassa Fever</data>
      <data key="d1">disease</data>
      <data key="d2">Lassa fever is another viral hemorrhagic fever that necessitates differential diagnosis with Marburg hemorrhagic fever.&lt;SEP&gt;Lassa fever is a disease caused by the Lassa virus.</data>
