    <node id="Medical Document">
      <data key="d0">Medical Document</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">The Medical Document is a type of clinical text that provides detailed information about specific health topics or conditions. It can be used to discuss secondary prevention strategies for various diseases, such as fungal meningitis. A medical document typically contains a written record of a patient's medical history, diagnosis, and treatment plan.

It may cover a wide range of medical topics, including acute bronchitis and congenital herpes. These documents often contain clinical details and treatment protocols for specific medical procedures, like Dermabrasion. The information within a medical document can be used to inform healthcare professionals about the best practices in treating various health conditions.

In summary, a Medical Document is an essential tool for healthcare providers and patients alike, serving as a reliable source of information on medical topics and treatments. By providing detailed clinical information, these documents aid in the delivery of high-quality patient care.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-edd7ac96b34c28b55c34f0dae83f6cf8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0157b8aee205333e2ffdb4843a873de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-104e30ec578f7f19e3c1af2cfb6529c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67f31fdeba3b08d8ffbbf3f423783bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-99459c884b05410676ea284f38d1224a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc45fed1d8c954d3edcef5f91e52bbb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1ecd676e66c2f16d35368912fa21958&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-48597b1d38d12727d8739dc61eee1f4c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2258cc9d8db0680e066bcf3b3675f10c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de6c3dde97de7b39b8a3073fde65281f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad48bb643563f87d4b1f99c073e3bb85&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-edd1b5df83b2e724f45910a954f75413&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d42bbf8dfa816d2d519b8c597b4c29ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7352dea9fdefc3ec7212dd4f88e8f77b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a108389c3f299fd71255c81b03305b55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-890ed5532260e84d43d5d4c567c6ab45</data>
