    <node id="Wiskott-Aldrich Syndrome">
      <data key="d0">Wiskott-Aldrich Syndrome</data>
      <data key="d1">condition</data>
      <data key="d2">Wiskott-Aldrich syndrome is a rare genetic disorder affecting primarily males, characterized by thrombocytopenia (low platelet count), eczema, and immunodeficiency due to mutations in the WAS gene.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e349119c3189688316f142a76b2f2e86</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
