      <data key="d0">Idiopathic Thrombocytopenic Purpura</data>
      <data key="d1">condition</data>
      <data key="d2">Idiopathic thrombocytopenic purpura (ITP) is a blood disorder characterized by low platelet count, often misdiagnosed as Bernard-Soulier syndrome.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e349119c3189688316f142a76b2f2e86</data>
