    <node id="Anticoagulant">
      <data key="d0">Anticoagulant</data>
      <data key="d1">other</data>
      <data key="d2">An anticoagulant medication that is used to prevent blood clotting.&lt;SEP&gt;Warfarin is an anticoagulant medication that works by inhibiting the production of vitamin K-dependent clotting factors in the liver, thereby preventing blood coagulation.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e349119c3189688316f142a76b2f2e86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3a0c8e154e4ccec7970a27ed87dde58</data>
