    <node id="Infection">
      <data key="d0">Infection</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Infection with Naegleria is an infrequent medical event that can have severe consequences if left untreated.&lt;SEP&gt;Toxoplasma infection occurs upon ingestion of contaminated food or raw meat.&lt;SEP&gt;An infection is an invasion of the body by microorganisms such as bacteria or viruses.&lt;SEP&gt;Severe infections can trigger physiological stress, increasing the risk of HHS.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-12f440140127265b2c2acfc6c8310641&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1282a35dc5da42f84a384a0de8a9c41d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-073142c11014525a0c579f8afe5d210b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18b3a59bf7f5ccc18f7641e35b20249f</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
