      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Non-specific reactive follicular hyperplasia (NSRFH) refers to a type of lymphadenopathy characterized by non-specific reactive changes in the lymphoid tissue.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-052d9f2eb36a76fdb7920ef60341853c</data>
