      <data key="d3">chunk-052d9f2eb36a76fdb7920ef60341853c</data>
      <data key="d2">Viral lymphadenopathy is caused by macrophage infiltration and lymphoid hyperplasia, often accompanied by other symptoms.&lt;SEP&gt;Viral lymphadenopathy is marked by macrophage infiltration and lymphoid hyperplasia.</data>
