    <node id="Immunocompromised Patients">
      <data key="d0">Immunocompromised Patients</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-052d9f2eb36a76fdb7920ef60341853c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6afd96faad2cc5882099be8abb7943d</data>
      <data key="d2">Necrosis can be observed in immunocompromised individuals, who are more susceptible to severe reactions from infections or diseases.&lt;SEP&gt;Patients who are immunocompromised face a higher risk of developing severe complications from Hepatitis E, such as chronic liver disease and other conditions.</data>
      <data key="d1">persongroup</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
