    <node id="Mitral Regurgitation">
      <data key="d0">Mitral Regurgitation</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Mitral regurgitation can lead to pulmonary edema and other complications.&lt;SEP&gt;Mitral regurgitation is a heart condition characterized by the leakage of blood flow from the left side of the heart.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-b2df8254abbb9c5202e43d9e23991b28&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0937f4b8bce4793fe181da12cd7f22c3</data>
