      <data key="d5">1776224770</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Chest Pain">
      <data key="d0">Chest Pain</data>
      <data key="d1">symptom</data>
      <data key="d2">Chest pain is a common symptom of ST-elevation myocardial infarction.&lt;SEP&gt;Palpitations are sometimes associated with chest pain, which can be a symptom of various underlying conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Reduced blood flow to the heart muscle causes chest pain in chronic cases.&lt;SEP&gt;Shortness of breath and wheezing are common manifestations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-b2df8254abbb9c5202e43d9e23991b28&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e521741147e08defca5beb7c20e86d2a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7c0f69e36eeb5da53429b84ed908e5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5970e312d13536cfdcd7ca01d35e2f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbe7a4df275280a24a14fa22f341095f</data>
