    <node id="Aplastic Anemia">
      <data key="d0">Aplastic Anemia</data>
      <data key="d1">disease</data>
      <data key="d2">Aplastic anemia is a complex disease with an unknown underlying cause and multiple genetic factors involved in its pathogenesis.&lt;SEP&gt;Aplastic anemia is a rare condition where the bone marrow fails to produce sufficient red blood cells, white blood cells, and platelets.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fcfeb24553a10cd0e61fdc71e0f554e8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc45fed1d8c954d3edcef5f91e52bbb2</data>
