    <node id="Immunity">
      <data key="d0">Immunity</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The regulation of immunity is critical in the pathogenesis of aplastic anemia, particularly through the actions of FOXP3 positive regulatory T cells.</data>
