    <node id="Colorectal Cancer">
      <data key="d0">Colorectal Cancer</data>
      <data key="d1">cancer</data>
      <data key="d2">Colorectal cancer is a type of cancer that affects the colon and rectum, with patients having IBD at increased risk but often diagnosed earlier than the general population through routine surveillance.&lt;SEP&gt;Colorectal cancer is a type of cancer that affects the colon and rectum.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-491c0761387cab9f81178653066edcbc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc45fed1d8c954d3edcef5f91e52bbb2</data>
