    <node id="Thunderclap Headache">
      <data key="d0">Thunderclap Headache</data>
      <data key="d1">symptom</data>
      <data key="d2">A thunderclap headache, also known as a "thunderclap headache," is often indicative of a subarachnoid hemorrhage.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5ddbc7f33848d62cd982cd6bdf687587</data>
