    </node>
    <node id="Seizure">
      <data key="d0">Seizure</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">A seizure can increase the likelihood of bleeding from an aneurysm in patients with subarachnoid hemorrhage.&lt;SEP&gt;A seizure is a sudden, involuntary muscle contraction or relaxation.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5ddbc7f33848d62cd982cd6bdf687587&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7fa41123c6e6925df4bb76974932747</data>
