    <node id="Antibodies">
      <data key="d0">Antibodies</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Antibodies are proteins that bind to specific antigens on the surface of red blood cells and cause hemolysis if present in excess.&lt;SEP&gt;Antibodies are proteins produced by B cells that recognize and bind to specific antigens.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-17717aab6acc128a83824d9e8317ea4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc45fed1d8c954d3edcef5f91e52bbb2</data>
