      <data key="d2">Losartan functions as an angiotensin II receptor blocker.&lt;SEP&gt;Losartan is an alternative medication for hypertension that rarely causes coughing.&lt;SEP&gt;Losartan is an angiotensin II receptor blocker used to treat hypertension and other conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Losartan is an angiotensin II receptor blocker used to treat high blood pressure and protect the kidneys from damage caused by diabetes.</data>
