      <data key="d1">causesgrowthhormonedeficiency</data>
      <data key="d2">Hypothyroidism is a condition of underactivity, typically caused by decreased production of thyroid hormones.&lt;SEP&gt;Hypothyroidism can contribute to the development of growth hormone deficiency and subsequent short stature.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-41c3680a3ad5516d5e6dcd6d045f4ed9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9f255691d2c2b02c84652be9d8c3d51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-865f279e1b6a3e8bf38bf34c9c655cb3</data>
