    <node id="Pleural Fluid">
      <data key="d0">Pleural Fluid</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">Pleural fluid is the fluid accumulated in the pleural space, which can interfere with various physical examination findings.&lt;SEP&gt;Pleural fluid is a type of body fluid that accumulates in the pleural space during empyema.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c16a4c902adb4dbeda6878a55d31bfe9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-743cfdf09792d3c6190a63afd0423e8d</data>
