      <data key="d0">Humerus Fracture</data>
      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">A humerus fracture occurs in younger patients who are skeletally immature and typically require open reduction for treatment.&lt;SEP&gt;The humerus fracture refers to a break or crack in the humerus bone.</data>
