    <node id="Hypertension">
      <data key="d0">Hypertension</data>
      <data key="d1">disease</data>
      <data key="d2">Hypertension, or high blood pressure, is the condition being treated by Chlorothiazide and Diuril.&lt;SEP&gt;Hypertension is a medical condition characterized by high blood pressure.&lt;SEP&gt;Hypertension is a major risk factor for developing metabolic syndrome.&lt;SEP&gt;High blood pressure, or hypertension, is the condition being treated by Lisinopril and Losartan.&lt;SEP&gt;Hypertension, or high blood pressure, is the condition being treated by Lisinopril and Losartan.</data>
