      <data key="d2">Corticosteroids are used in the treatment protocol for patients with neoplastic meningitis who receive intrathecal chemotherapy.&lt;SEP&gt;Corticosteroids are medications used to reduce inflammation and swelling in the body.</data>
      <data key="d1">medicationtype</data>
