    </node>
    <node id="Cardiovascular Disease">
      <data key="d0">Cardiovascular Disease</data>
      <data key="d1">disease</data>
      <data key="d2">Cardiovascular disease refers to a range of conditions that affect the heart and blood vessels.&lt;SEP&gt;Cardiovascular disease encompasses a range of conditions that affect the heart and circulatory system, including high blood pressure.&lt;SEP&gt;Cardiovascular disease is a condition linked to menopause due to estrogen deficiency, causing vasoconstriction and increased risk.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-14491e922b3c111ccfd99b482d34948b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81ca909fcf7ec8b326421ab4d2766d19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e80dc7bcd1293375ca72b55372764fe1</data>
