    <node id="Purkinje Network">
      <data key="d0">Purkinje Network</data>
      <data key="d1">naturalobject</data>
      <data key="d2">The Purkinje network is a complex system of fibers that transmit electrical impulses from the atria to the ventricles in the heart.</data>
