      <data key="d0">Autonomic Nervous System</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The autonomic nervous system (ANS) is a branch of the nervous system that controls involuntary bodily functions, including heart rate.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-0d9df8319256ab3c418f8c73ac00fad8</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1776215601</data>
