      <data key="d0">Fabry's Disease</data>
      <data key="d1">medicalprocedure</data>
      <data key="d2">Fabry's disease is a genetic disorder that affects the ability of red blood cells to break down a type of fat called globotriaosylsphingosine (Lyso-Gb3).</data>
