    <node id="Palpitations">
      <data key="d0">Palpitations</data>
      <data key="d1">symptom</data>
      <data key="d2">Palpitations are a nonspecific symptom that are often defined as a rapid disagreeable sensation / pulsation that may be momentary or sustained and regular or irregular.&lt;SEP&gt;Palpitations are irregular heartbeats that can be perceived by the person experiencing them.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e521741147e08defca5beb7c20e86d2a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d5d870ad6493ac1d369fb7c8bf144bb</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
