    <node id="Immunosuppression">
      <data key="d0">Immunosuppression</data>
      <data key="d1">condition</data>
      <data key="d2">Immunosuppression is a medical condition where the immune system's effectiveness is reduced due to disease or treatment.&lt;SEP&gt;Immunosuppression increases the risk of disseminated histoplasmosis infection due to weakened immune systems.|</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-dc45fed1d8c954d3edcef5f91e52bbb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09c5fd73265ac4666b40e031048cf9c4</data>
