    <node id="Cardiac Rehabilitation">
      <data key="d0">Cardiac Rehabilitation</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">Cardiac rehabilitation is a medically supervised program that helps patients with coronary artery disease improve their heart health and reduce symptoms.&lt;SEP&gt;Cardiac rehabilitation refers to a medically supervised program aimed at improving cardiovascular health through exercise, education, and behavioral modification.</data>
