      <data key="d1">medicalprocedure</data>
      <data key="d2">A CT scan is an imaging test used to visualize internal body structures and detect abnormalities, such as tumors.&lt;SEP&gt;A CT scan provides detailed images of the chest to help diagnose empyema and its causes.&lt;SEP&gt;Computerized Tomography (CT) scans can provide additional diagnostic information for lumbosacral hemangioma when used alongside MRI.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7635b390410b3ab22d8fdc263585cac7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-743cfdf09792d3c6190a63afd0423e8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-350836c0cbd5f38144bfd64dc2e11cd0</data>
