      <data key="d0">Metabolic Conditions</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-af76a19d7c4899519758f59183dd1222</data>
      <data key="d2">Both metabolic and infectious conditions increase the risk of a poor prognosis when combined with mental disorders.</data>
