    <node id="Intracoronary Imaging">
      <data key="d0">Intracoronary Imaging</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Intracoronary imaging techniques such as intravascular ultrasound (IVUS) or optical coherence tomography (OCT) may provide complementary information for establishing a definitive diagnosis of SCAD.</data>
