      <data key="d0">Coronary Computed Tomography Angiography</data>
      <data key="d1">diagnostictool</data>
      <data key="d2">CCTA is a non-invasive imaging technique that can help diagnose and monitor SCAD, particularly in cases involving proximal or large-caliber coronary arteries.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a93edc44f777282915e371c46fed58c1</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
