      <data key="d0">Optical Coherence Tomography</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Optical coherence tomography (OCT) is a medical imaging technique that uses low-coherence interferometry to produce high-resolution images of the inner structure of blood vessels.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a93edc44f777282915e371c46fed58c1</data>
