    <edge source="Warfarin" target="Aspirin">
      <data key="d7">11.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Aspirin and Warfarin are two medications that, when taken together, create a dangerous drug interaction. This interaction increases the risk of gastrointestinal bleeding. It is essential to be aware of this potential hazard when taking either medication.

The combination of Aspirin with Warfarin results in a significant increase in the risk of bleeding complications. Both medications affect blood clotting and can exacerbate each other's effects, leading to serious health issues.

Aspirin and Warfarin are both used to treat various medical conditions, such as pain relief and blood thinning. However, their interaction is a critical consideration when prescribing or taking these medications.

The risk of gastrointestinal bleeding associated with Aspirin and Warfarin can be severe and even life-threatening. Patients taking either medication should be closely monitored for signs of bleeding and have regular blood tests to ensure that the medications are not interacting negatively.

It is worth noting that while there may be some redundancy in the descriptions provided, the core message remains consistent: taking Aspirin with Warfarin creates a dangerous drug interaction that increases the risk of gastrointestinal bleeding.&lt;SEP&gt;Combining Aspirin with Warfarin creates a dangerous drug interaction.&lt;SEP&gt;Taking Aspirin concurrently with Warfarin creates a dangerous drug interaction.&lt;SEP&gt;Combining Aspirin with Warfarin creates a significant anticoagulant effect.</data>
      <data key="d9">adverse interaction,concomitant medication,contraction,contradication,contraindication,drug interaction,potential interaction</data>
      <data key="d10">chunk-58ce513efff4e4279006c76309bbe13e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a45c0433e861eaa94dbda4172985c8d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7361a603e8f2f0aa1358a337cf72e362&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e349119c3189688316f142a76b2f2e86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96246f0053db41bc6854767c93a37e6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e29dee1ec3e83daa8c3982ec784f54d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a72bff6a2caadef59875d68cb6aee2c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c4689566af7f5f15132f08d3ceb0561&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2258cc9d8db0680e066bcf3b3675f10c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18b3a59bf7f5ccc18f7641e35b20249f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bfa6d6104ce651a3fa698d413435e00</data>
