    </edge>
    <edge source="Posterior Aortic Sinus" target="Non-Coronary Sinus">
      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The non-coronary sinus is also known as the posterior aortic sinus due to its lack of connections to coronary arteries.</data>
