    </edge>
    <edge source="Friction" target="Radiation">
      <data key="d7">2.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Ionizing radiation from X-rays or gamma rays can also cause friction-related burns due to rough skin or synthetic fibers.&lt;SEP&gt;Rough skin or synthetic fibers from friction can cause damage to the tissues similar to radiation burns.</data>
      <data key="d9">cause,type</data>
