    <edge source="Perinicious Anemia" target="Bipolar Disorder">
      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Bipolar disorder appears to be genetically linked to pernicious anemia, a hereditary form of Vitamin B12 deficiency.</data>
