    <edge source="Bipolar Disorder" target="Catatonia">
      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Catatonia is often associated with bipolar disorder and can be specified when symptoms meet criteria for catatonia during the course of a neurodevelopmental or psychotic disorder.</data>
