    </edge>
    <edge source="Catatonia" target="Schizophrenia">
      <data key="d7">2.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Schizophrenia can manifest with symptoms similar to catatonia, such as posturing and mannerism.&lt;SEP&gt;In cases of catatonia, schizophrenia is considered an associated mental disorder.</data>
